~~ Notification Capstone ~~
This work is for a WPI Capstone Project, and aims to function as a fully developed SDK.

~~ Installation ~~
Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/abmartin25/Notifaction-Capstone.git
cd Notification-Capstone

Install Relevant Dependancies:
This project requires the node.js runtime environment to be present, which is done via an external install
https://nodejs.org/en

~~ Usage ~~
1. Electron:
  npx electron-rebuild -f -w better-sqlite3
  python sentinel.py for users
2. Debugging:
  npm rebuild better-sqlite3 --update-binary
  python sentinel.py   --debug 
~~ OLD ~~
1. npm install better-sqlite3
2. npm install --save-dev electron@latest
3. npm install express --save
4. npm install python-shell
5. npm start
-> If there is a NODE_MODULE_VERSION mismatch try
6. npx electron-rebuild -f -w better-sqlite3 ?
2. npm start

~ Testing ~
1. npx playwright test
--debug to watch 
-- grep @debug to watch specified test

